4:05 pm cases 22CF1027, 22CM613 called. Defendant Shaun M. Dorsey in court, in custody.  Attorney Rachel Allison Robole in court for Shaun M. Dorsey.  Attorney Afton Brianna Lewis in court for State of Wisconsin.  
Dr. Dileep Borra appears by video. State in compliance with victim notification requirements. Defendant makes a statement regarding his competency. State calls Dr. Borra to testify- is sworn and testifies. 
Cross examination by the Defense. Re-direct by the State. Re-cross by the Defense. 
Court: Court finds the defendant not competent but likely to regain competence. 
Defense objects. Court finds State has met their burden.
